text: The 10-day forecasts suggest very little increase from the 5-day forecasts, especially for those predicted by the GLM and Richards model (Figure 1 ). Average 10-day forecasts predict between 1306-1322 cumulative cases with upper bounds ranging from 1410-1748 cases. These forecasts suggest that an additional 65-81 cases (UB: 169-507) will be reported by 23 February 2020.
